  "raw_block": "–General scriptures concerningPs 19:7-9;119:1-8;Pr \n28:4,5;Mt 22:21;Lu 16:17;20:22-25;Ro 2:14,15;7:7,12,14;13:10;1Ti 1:5,8-10;Jas 1:25;1Jo 3:4;5:3\n–SeeLITIGATION\n–SeeCOMMANDMENTS\n–SeeDUTY TO GOD\n–OF MOSES\n–(Contained in the books of Exodus, Leviticus, Numbers, and Deuteronomy)\n  .Given at SinaiEx 19;De 1:1;4:10-13;33:2;Hab 3:3\n  .Received by the disposition of angelsDe 33:2;Ps 68:17;Ac 7:53;Ga 3:19;Heb 2:2\n  .Was given because of transgressions until the Messiah arrivedGa 3:19\n  .Engraved on stoneEx 20:3-17; with 24:12; 31:18; 32:16; 34:29; 40:20;De 4:13;5:4-22;9:10\n  .SeeTABLES\n  .SeeCOMMANDMENTS\n  .Preserved in the ark of the covenantEx 25:16;De 31:9,26\n  .Found by Hilkiah in the house of the Lord2Ki 22:8\n  .Engraved upon monumentsDe 27:2-8;Jos 8:30-35\n  .To be written\n  .On door postsDe 6:9;11:20\n  .On frontlets for the forehead, and parchment for the handEx 13:9,16;De 6:4-9;11:18-21\n  .Children instructed in\n  .SeeCHILDREN\n  .SeeINSTRUCTION\n  .Expounded by\n  .The priests and Levite",
